23,3276928],"comment_count":0,"is_following":false,"excerpt":"是否存在不合理的出资运营比例和不可持续的营收模式问题？ 该政府决算写得非常详尽，但是最终营收是亏损的 几个重要赞助商中百岁山赞助饮用水，李宁赞助工作人员衣物，斯蒂卡赞助球桌，英利奥铺地板，地胶赞助只有500平方米，剩下的1500平方米竟然需要额外支付 微博、抖音等相关数据都作为打分依据，但是关键词是互动率偏低，合理怀疑宣发费用的合理性和投资回报 门票预期收入仅80万，广告收入目标是增加（是说＞0？实际收入仅23万），外地球迷人均消费＞2000的情况下，撬动了815万的的财政支出 票房收入为何不能及时交付财政？ 简而言之从财务角度来说，太原出了70万刀是版权费，也就是WTT的收入，WTT只出了7.5万刀奖金，即WTT的成本，除了这个基本上WTT是纯收入，能做成亏损匪夷所思 以上为摘取的部分结论，相关报告梳理的完整链接来源如下：https://czt.shanxi.gov.cn/bmp_upfiles/site/gfa/upfiles/GFA02/2023/e510e00ff7ac4bf2bc81f02be966afac/0c2aaddc-6e83-4cbb-b6b1-e69a576a5583.pdf"},"attached_info":"CkEIhILru4XggL9OEAMaCTExMjc3MjE0NCD//PO7BjAAOOwFQBNyCjg5Nzg0NTcwNzd4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA==","detail_text":"52 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-4302ef8d0fe898cbf084d0780dea5738_720w.png"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"20_1736453998.927450","card_id":"Q_9071328724","target":{"id":9071328724,"title":"如何看待多益网络要求员工退还3年餐费44490元？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/9071328724","type":"question","created":1736332318,"answer_count":86,"follower_count":211,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[1068,2566,415712,2835776],"comment_count":0,"is_following":false,"excerpt":"天下没有免费的午餐，公司没有免费的食堂"},"attached_info":"CkEIhILru4XggL9OEAMaCTExMjc5MDg5NCCeqPm7BjAAONMBQBRyCjkwNzEzMjg3MjR4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA==","detail_text":"52 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/v2-95420c91b5c836dae2c33cf7244af8f7_b.jpg"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"21_1736453998.927724","card_id":"Q_5676021525","target":{"id":5676021525,"title":"博士生周末会休息吗？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/5676021525","type":"question","created":1733067395,"answer_count":241,"follower_count":287,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","